long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Easily copy git branch name from your jira ticket 

`cmd + .` or `ctrl + .` will copy git branch name from the jira ticket in the format:

`<issueType>/<issueNumber>-<issueSummary>`
